    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously cared for since day one. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and absolutely no scratches, chips, or dents. Inside, the cabin is pristine, featuring premium materials that show zero signs of wear and still retain that new-car scent. Mechanically, it is perfect, offering a smooth and powerful driving experience that feels as if it just rolled off the assembly line. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer seeking a vehicle in peak collector-quality condition.",
