    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Attention DIY enthusiasts and bargain hunters! This vehicle is looking for a new owner who isn't afraid of a little project. While it is in poor condition and will require some mechanical attention and TLC to get it back to its best, it represents a fantastic, budget-friendly opportunity to own a vehicle with potential!",
