      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts as it should, making it a reliable choice for any driver. While the exterior and interior show some minor signs of normal wear and tear consistent with its age, the car is clean and presents very well. It is a solid, dependable vehicle that is ready for its next owner without needing immediate major repairs.",
