    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional vehicle maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This unit remains in pristine, showroom-quality condition, exhibiting no discernible wear. Meticulously serviced and preserved, it represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands uncompromising quality. Experience a standard of luxury and performance that aligns perfectly with its original factory specifications.",
